ActJobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day after the Day on which this Order is made as the Day on which Paragraph 21.52(1)(b) of the National Housing Act Comes into Force and July 1, 2013 as the Day on which Sections 361 to 364 of the Jobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder (1) fixing the day after the day on which the Order is made as the day on which a provision of section 356 of the JOBS, GROWTH AND LONG-TERM PROSPERITY ACT, chapter 19 of the Statutes of Canada COMES INTO FORCE; and (2) fixing July 1, 2013 as the date on which sections 361 to 364 of the same Act COME INTO FORCE.
